### Get list all studios (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/studios HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get list all studios (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/studios?page=1&limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Add studio
POST http://localhost:5000/api/studios HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New studio",
  "location": "Los Angeles",
  "foundationYear": 2025,
  "logo": "",
  "about": ""
}

### Get studio by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/studios/37 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Edit studio by ID
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/studios/37 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated studio",
  "location": "",
  "foundationYear": "",
  "logo": "",
  "about": ""
}

### Remove studio by ID
DELETE  http://localhost:5000/api/studios/37 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
